New Zealand Condemns Japanese Whaling Program in Southern Ocean

-- B y   C h r i s   B o u r k e
-- 
2011-10-04T22:50:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-04/new-zealand-condemns-japanese-whaling-program-in-southern-ocean.html
New Zealand ’s government has
condemned  Japan ’s decision to resume whaling in the Southern
Ocean, according to an e-mailed statement from Foreign Affairs
Minister Murray McCully. The decision is “disrespectful” of
strong concerns expressed by the Australian and New Zealand
people, he said in the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Bourke at 
 cbourke4@bloomberg.net  